### Important SQL Learnings
- COUNT(*) measures rows/orders
- SUM(quantity) measures total items sold
- Revenue requires:
  quantity × price
- WHERE filters rows before SELECT
- HAVING filters grouped/aggregated results
- Correct business metric selection is critical in analytics
- Simplifying unnecessary joins improves query quality

